            "title": "今日我咁睇｜美伊談判未有進展 惟擴大戰事機會不大 港股料跑贏｜小編苟豪",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ANAyEkAuBycenly19iSzKA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/5283c824d4f8b5c6ba68ed76509d1460\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><ol class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-decimal\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗談判沒有突破，不過美國總統特朗普指暫緩不炸伊朗能源設施，油價昨日先升後升幅收窄。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-decimal\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美股昨日調整明顯，但考慮到戰事進一步擴大的機會有限，美股預期會有反彈，選股可以考慮明星芯片股如英偉達、Intel、AMD等。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-decimal\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">港股方面，AI大模型股昨日隨大市下跌，可以考慮開始分批買入，而外賣平台股如美團、阿里巴巴亦可以考慮。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-decimal\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">指數方面，預計恆指在24800點整固，25200點的阻力未有突破，阻力逐步加大，而24500的支持應該不錯。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-decimal\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">恆指牛熊證街貨，牛證比例偏低，雖然未低於熊證，但相反理論來看是中性偏好。</p></li></ol></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E6%88%91%E5%92%81%E7%9D%87-%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E6%9C%AA%E6%9C%89%E9%80%B2%E5%B1%95-%E6%83%9F%E6%93%B4%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%B0%E4%BA%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%A7-%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E6%96%99%E8%B7%91%E8%B4%8F-%E5%B0%8F%E7%B7%A8%E8%8B%9F%E8%B1%AA-020000517.html",
